## 2026-04-10 - US-005
- **What was implement..."
All acceptance criteria are met:

- `src/checker.ts` exports `checkRepo` and `spawnCheck` with the correct signatures
- `checkRepo` returns cached skills when hash unchanged, clones + discovers folders when hash changes, updates cache, cleans up temp dir in all cases, and silently returns `[]` on any git failure
- `GIT_TERMINAL_PROMPT=0` is set on all git subprocess calls
- `spawnCheck` short-circuits when disabled or rate-limited, merges/deduplicates repos, evicts uninstalled skills from `notified_skills`, calls `showToast` only when new skills found
- All 6 unit tests pass (plus 3 pre-existing test suites, 22 total)
